;mycomment
BLK FORM 0.1 Z X-50 Y-25 Z-50
BLK FORM 0.2 X+50 Y+25 Z+1
;-------------------------------------
;The postprocessor uses the following settings for CYCLE19:
;  Make sure that these settings match the settings on your machine.
;  MP7500 Bit1: 0 - Machine angles
;  MP7500 Bit2: 1 - The tilting axes are positioned with CYCLE19
;-------------------------------------
;WARNING, Risk of collision detected.
;  5-axis simultaneous machining has been detected in this program
;  and the 'Tilted Workplane' property is set to 'use Cycle19'.
;  With CYCLE19, we cannot guarantee that safe prepositioning is possible
;  without knowing the actual machine settings.
;  For this reason, the postprocessor will use PLANE SPATIAL for prepositioning
;  5-axis simultaneous toolpaths.
M0
